so, the imposition of shear strain and\nthereby vorticity on the counterflow can be substantial indicating the need for\nflamelet models with both shear strain and normal strain.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 May 2020 21:53:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-16"}
