 expressive power\nof hybrid automaton in security risk assessment, the hazard development time\nand its impact on cyber security design, and the tight coupling between the\nphysical and the cyber systems for CPS that requires an integrated design\napproach to achieve cost-effective and secure designs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 May 2020 02:08:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-29"}
