locity field can be altered by changing both electrolyte concentration and\nsymmetry. However, applying VG was found to be a more efficient way than\nelectrolyte modifications. This includes generating circulation inside the\nchannel which is of prime importance for applications such as mixing or\nseparation/trapping.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 May 2020 17:22:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-01"}
